	* how-startup-shutdown-works.txt: Add new document.

2010-01-29  Corinna Vinschen  <corinna@vinschen.de>

	* sec_auth.cc (lsaauth): Use CYG_LSA_MAGIC as checksum start value to
	decouple from Cygwin release.

